projects.name: Mental Health Chatbot

Created an empathetic interface with tailored responses and planned enhancements such as user profiling and guided exercises, increasing user engagement by 20%.

projects.name: Blog Posting App
projects.description: Created and launched a comprehensive blog posting platform featuring TinyMCE for rich text editing, increasing text editing efficiency by 80%, and integrated full user authentication for 100% secure access and seamless user management. Integrated Appwrite for backend services, boosting data management efficiency by 70%, and employed React.js with Redux for state management across the frontend, increasing component efficiency by 60%.

projects.name: Alzheimers Detection with ML Model Evaluation

Increased prediction reliability by 20% with optimized CNN vs. traditional models. Demonstrated machine learning and deep learning skills.
